ater into mixing bowl. Place Varoma with pudding basin into position, secure Varoma lid and steam <b>60 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>."},{"content":"Remove Varoma and add remaining 1500 g water into mixing bowl. Place Varoma back into position, secure Varoma lid and steam <b>70 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>. Allow pudding to rest in basin for 40 minutes, then turn out onto a plate. Serve warm with pouring cream or custard (see Tips)."}],"hintsAndTricks":["To make your own vegan butter, pouring cream and custard, refer to the recipes on this recipe chip.","You can find stem ginger at specialty food stores and online."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","3h 5m","4 portions"]}